videos.headline: Bearcats score easy TD on QB option
videos.description: Cincinnati QB Desmond Ridder fakes the handoff and goes untouched for a 13-yard touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Bearcats score easy TD on QB option) 2019/10/12

videos.headline: Ridder airs it out for 75-yard Cincinnati TD
videos.description: Desmond Ridder goes deep to a wide-open Rashad Medaris for a 75-yard score.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Ridder airs it out for 75-yard Cincinnati TD) 2019/10/12

videos.headline: Deguara stiff-arms his way into the end zone for Cincinnati
videos.description: Desmond Ridder checks it down to Josiah Deguara for the 15-yard touchdown to extend Cincinnati's lead on Houston.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Deguara stiff-arms his way into the end zone for Cincinnati) 2019/10/12

videos.headline: Tune floats one deep to Stevenson for the TD
videos.description: Clayton Tune airs it out to Marquez Stevenson for the 69-yard touchdown to trim Houston's deficit against Cincinnati.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Tune floats one deep to Stevenson for the TD) 2019/10/12
